### 1. Registrar usuário
POST http://localhost:5001/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123",
  "email": "admin@admin.com"
}

### 2. Login e obter token
POST http://localhost:5001/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### ⚠️ Copie o token retornado e substitua no Authorization abaixo ⚠️
@token=eyJhbGciOi...

### 3. Criar produto
POST http://localhost:5002/api/Products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Notebook Dell",
  "description": "Notebook i7 16GB RAM",
  "price": 5500.00,
  "stock": 50
}

### 4. Listar produtos (sem token)
GET http://localhost:5002/api/Products
Accept: application/json

### 5. Buscar produto por ID
GET http://localhost:5002/api/Products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Criar pedido
POST http://localhost:5003/api/Orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2, "price": 5500.00 }
  ]
}

### 7. Listar pedidos (só Admin)
GET http://localhost:5003/api/Orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Buscar pedido por ID
GET http://localhost:5003/api/Orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


#Registrar/Login → pega token

#Criar produtos → só Admin autorizado

#Criar pedidos → qualquer usuário autenticado